{"data":[{"name":"37:1","price":"以列班者发誓，","arabic":"وَٱلصَّٰٓفَّٰتِ صَفّٗا","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3789,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:2","price":"以驱策者发誓，","arabic":"فَٱلزَّٰجِرَٰتِ زَجۡرٗا","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3790,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:3","price":"以诵读教诲者发誓，","arabic":"فَٱلتَّٰلِيَٰتِ ذِكۡرًا","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3791,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:4","price":"你们所当崇拜的，确是独一的","arabic":"إِنَّ إِلَٰهَكُمۡ لَوَٰحِدٞ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3792,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:5","price":"他是天地万物之主，是一切东方的主。","arabic":"رَّبُّ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَمَا بَيۡنَهُمَا وَرَبُّ ٱلۡمَشَٰرِقِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3793,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:6","price":"我确已用文采即繁星点缀最近的天，","arabic":"إِنَّا زَيَّنَّا ٱلسَّمَآءَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا بِزِينَةٍ ٱلۡكَوَاكِبِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3794,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:7","price":"我对一切叛逆的恶魔保护它，","arabic":"وَحِفۡظٗا مِّن كُلِّ شَيۡطَٰنٖ مَّارِدٖ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3795,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:8","price":"他们不得窃听上界的众天使，他们自各方被射击，","arabic":"لَّا يَسَّمَّعُونَ إِلَى ٱلۡمَلَإِ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ وَيُقۡذَفُونَ مِن كُلِّ جَانِبٖ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3796,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:9","price":"被驱逐，他们将受永久的刑罚。","arabic":"دُحُورٗاۖ وَلَهُمۡ عَذَابٞ وَاصِبٌ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3797,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:10","price":"但窃听一次的，灿烂的流星就追赶上他。","arabic":"إِلَّا مَنۡ خَطِفَ ٱلۡخَطۡفَةَ فَأَتۡبَعَهُۥ شِهَابٞ ثَاقِبٞ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3798,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:11","price":"你问他们吧！究竟是他们更难造呢？还是我所创造的更难造呢？我确已用粘泥创造了他们，","arabic":"فَٱسۡتَفۡتِهِمۡ أَهُمۡ أَشَدُّ خَلۡقًا أَم مَّنۡ خَلَقۡنَآۚ إِنَّا خَلَقۡنَٰهُم مِّن طِينٖ لَّازِبِۭ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3799,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:12","price":"不然！你感到惊奇，而他们却嘲笑。","arabic":"بَلۡ عَجِبۡتَ وَيَسۡخَرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3800,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:13","price":"他们虽闻教诲，却不觉悟。","arabic":"وَإِذَا ذُكِّرُواْ لَا يَذۡكُرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3801,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:14","price":"他们虽见迹象，却加以嘲笑","arabic":"وَإِذَا رَأَوۡاْ ءَايَةٗ يَسۡتَسۡخِرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3802,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:15","price":"他们说：“这个只是明显的魔术。","arabic":"وَقَالُوٓاْ إِنۡ هَٰذَآ إِلَّا سِحۡرٞ مُّبِينٌ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3803,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:16","price":"难道我们死后，已变为尘土和朽骨的时候，必定复活吗？","arabic":"أَءِذَا مِتۡنَا وَكُنَّا تُرَابٗا وَعِظَٰمًا أَءِنَّا لَمَبۡعُوثُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3804,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:17","price":"连我们的祖先，也要复活吗？”","arabic":"أَوَءَابَآؤُنَا ٱلۡأَوَّلُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3805,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:18","price":"你说：“是的！你们都要卑贱地被复活。”","arabic":"قُلۡ نَعَمۡ وَأَنتُمۡ دَٰخِرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3806,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:19","price":"才听见一声呐喊，他们就瞻望着，","arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا هِيَ زَجۡرَةٞ وَٰحِدَةٞ فَإِذَا هُمۡ يَنظُرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3807,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:20","price":"他们说：“伤哉我们！这就是报应之日。”","arabic":"وَقَالُواْ يَٰوَيۡلَنَا هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3808,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:21","price":"这就是你们所否认的判决之日。","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ ٱلَّذِي كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3809,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:22","price":"你们应当集合不义者和他们的伴侣，以及他们舍安拉而崇拜的，","arabic":"۞ ٱحۡشُرُواْ ٱلَّذِينَ ظَلَمُواْ وَأَزۡوَٰجَهُمۡ وَمَا كَانُواْ يَعۡبُدُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3810,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:23","price":"然后指示他们火狱的道路，","arabic":"مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ فَٱهۡدُوهُمۡ إِلَىٰ صِرَٰطِ ٱلۡجَحِيمِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3811,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:24","price":"并拦住他们，因为他们的确要受审问。","arabic":"وَقِفُوهُمۡۖ إِنَّهُم مَّسۡـُٔولُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3812,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:25","price":"你们怎么不互助呢？","arabic":"مَا لَكُمۡ لَا تَنَاصَرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3813,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:26","price":"不然！他们在今日是归顺的。","arabic":"بَلۡ هُمُ ٱلۡيَوۡمَ مُسۡتَسۡلِمُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3814,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:27","price":"于是他们大家走向前来，互相谈论，","arabic":"وَأَقۡبَلَ بَعۡضُهُمۡ عَلَىٰ بَعۡضٖ يَتَسَآءَلُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3815,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:28","price":"这些人说：“你们确已用权力胁迫我们。”","arabic":"قَالُوٓاْ إِنَّكُمۡ كُنتُمۡ تَأۡتُونَنَا عَنِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3816,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:29","price":"那些人说：“不然！你们自己原来不是信道者，","arabic":"قَالُواْ بَل لَّمۡ تَكُونُواْ مُؤۡمِنِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3817,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:30","price":"我们对你们绝无权力。不然！你们是悖逆的民众。","arabic":"وَمَا كَانَ لَنَا عَلَيۡكُم مِّن سُلۡطَٰنِۭۖ بَلۡ كُنتُمۡ قَوۡمٗا طَٰغِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3818,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:31","price":"故我们应当受我们的主的判决，我们确是尝试的。","arabic":"فَحَقَّ عَلَيۡنَا قَوۡلُ رَبِّنَآۖ إِنَّا لَذَآئِقُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3819,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:32","price":"所以我们使你们迷误，我们自己也确实是迷误的。”","arabic":"فَأَغۡوَيۡنَٰكُمۡ إِنَّا كُنَّا غَٰوِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3820,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:33","price":"在那日，他们必定同受刑罚。","arabic":"فَإِنَّهُمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ فِي ٱلۡعَذَابِ مُشۡتَرِكُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3821,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:34","price":"我必定这样对待犯罪者。","arabic":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَفۡعَلُ بِٱلۡمُجۡرِمِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3822,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:35","price":"他们确是这样的：有人对他们说：“除安拉外，绝无应受崇拜的，”他们就忘自尊大，","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُوٓاْ إِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمۡ لَآ إِلَٰهَ إِلَّا ٱللَّهُ يَسۡتَكۡبِرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3823,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:36","price":"并且说：“难道我们务必要为一个狂妄的诗人，而抛弃我们的众神灵吗？”","arabic":"وَيَقُولُونَ أَئِنَّا لَتَارِكُوٓاْ ءَالِهَتِنَا لِشَاعِرٖ مَّجۡنُونِۭ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3824,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:37","price":"不然！他昭示了真理，并证实了历代的使者。","arabic":"بَلۡ جَآءَ بِٱلۡحَقِّ وَصَدَّقَ ٱلۡمُرۡسَلِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3825,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:38","price":"你们必定尝试痛苦的刑罚，","arabic":"إِنَّكُمۡ لَذَآئِقُواْ ٱلۡعَذَابِ ٱلۡأَلِيمِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3826,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:39","price":"你们只依自己的行为而受报酬。","arabic":"وَمَا تُجۡزَوۡنَ إِلَّا مَا كُنتُمۡ تَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3827,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:40","price":"惟安拉的虔诚的众仆，","arabic":"إِلَّا عِبَادَ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُخۡلَصِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3828,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:41","price":"将享受一种可知的给养——","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ لَهُمۡ رِزۡقٞ مَّعۡلُومٞ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3829,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:42","price":"各种水果，同时他们是受优待的；","arabic":"فَوَٰكِهُ وَهُم مُّكۡرَمُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3830,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:43","price":"他们在恩泽的乐园中，","arabic":"فِي جَنَّٰتِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3831,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:44","price":"他们坐在床上，彼此相对；","arabic":"عَلَىٰ سُرُرٖ مُّتَقَٰبِلِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3832,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:45","price":"有人以杯子在他们之间挨次传递，杯中满盛醴泉，","arabic":"يُطَافُ عَلَيۡهِم بِكَأۡسٖ مِّن مَّعِينِۭ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3833,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:46","price":"颜色洁白，饮者无不称为美味；","arabic":"بَيۡضَآءَ لَذَّةٖ لِّلشَّٰرِبِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3834,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:47","price":"醴泉中无麻醉物，他们也不因它而酩酊；","arabic":"لَا فِيهَا غَوۡلٞ وَلَا هُمۡ عَنۡهَا يُنزَفُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3835,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:48","price":"他们将有不视非礼的、美目的伴侣，","arabic":"وَعِندَهُمۡ قَٰصِرَٰتُ ٱلطَّرۡفِ عِينٞ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3836,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:49","price":"她们仿佛被珍藏的鸵卵样；","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُنَّ بَيۡضٞ مَّكۡنُونٞ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3837,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:50","price":"于是他们走向前来，互相谈论。","arabic":"فَأَقۡبَلَ بَعۡضُهُمۡ عَلَىٰ بَعۡضٖ يَتَسَآءَلُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3838,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:51","price":"他们中有一个人说：“我有一个朋友，","arabic":"قَالَ قَآئِلٞ مِّنۡهُمۡ إِنِّي كَانَ لِي قَرِينٞ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3839,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:52","price":"他问我：‘你确是诚信的吗？","arabic":"يَقُولُ أَءِنَّكَ لَمِنَ ٱلۡمُصَدِّقِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3840,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:53","price":"难道我们死后，已变为尘土和朽骨的时候，还必定要受报酬吗？’”","arabic":"أَءِذَا مِتۡنَا وَكُنَّا تُرَابٗا وَعِظَٰمًا أَءِنَّا لَمَدِينُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3841,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:54","price":"他说：“你们愿看他吗？”","arabic":"قَالَ هَلۡ أَنتُم مُّطَّلِعُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3842,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:55","price":"他俯视下面，就看见他在火狱的中央，","arabic":"فَٱطَّلَعَ فَرَءَاهُ فِي سَوَآءِ ٱلۡجَحِيمِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3843,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:56","price":"他说：“以安拉发誓，你的确几乎陷害了我。","arabic":"قَالَ تَٱللَّهِ إِن كِدتَّ لَتُرۡدِينِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3844,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:57","price":"如果没有我的主的恩惠，我必在被拘禁者之列。","arabic":"وَلَوۡلَا نِعۡمَةُ رَبِّي لَكُنتُ مِنَ ٱلۡمُحۡضَرِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3845,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:58","price":"我们不是再死的吗？","arabic":"أَفَمَا نَحۡنُ بِمَيِّتِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3846,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:59","price":"唯有我们初次的死亡，而我们绝不会受惩罚吗？","arabic":"إِلَّا مَوۡتَتَنَا ٱلۡأُولَىٰ وَمَا نَحۡنُ بِمُعَذَّبِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3847,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:60","price":"这确是伟大的成功，","arabic":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَهُوَ ٱلۡفَوۡزُ ٱلۡعَظِيمُ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3848,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:61","price":"工作者应当为获得这样的成功而工作。”","arabic":"لِمِثۡلِ هَٰذَا فَلۡيَعۡمَلِ ٱلۡعَٰمِلُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3849,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:62","price":"那是更善的款待呢？还是攒楛树？","arabic":"أَذَٰلِكَ خَيۡرٞ نُّزُلًا أَمۡ شَجَرَةُ ٱلزَّقُّومِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3850,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:63","price":"我以它为不义者的折磨。","arabic":"إِنَّا جَعَلۡنَٰهَا فِتۡنَةٗ لِّلظَّٰلِمِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3851,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:64","price":"它是在火狱底生长的一棵树，","arabic":"إِنَّهَا شَجَرَةٞ تَخۡرُجُ فِيٓ أَصۡلِ ٱلۡجَحِيمِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3852,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:65","price":"它的花篦，仿佛魔头。","arabic":"طَلۡعُهَا كَأَنَّهُۥ رُءُوسُ ٱلشَّيَٰطِينِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3853,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:66","price":"他们必定要吃那些果实，而以它充实肚腹。","arabic":"فَإِنَّهُمۡ لَأٓكِلُونَ مِنۡهَا فَمَالِـُٔونَ مِنۡهَا ٱلۡبُطُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3854,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:67","price":"然后他们必定要在那些果实上加饮沸水的混汤，","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ لَهُمۡ عَلَيۡهَا لَشَوۡبٗا مِّنۡ حَمِيمٖ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3855,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:68","price":"然后他们必定归于火狱。","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ مَرۡجِعَهُمۡ لَإِلَى ٱلۡجَحِيمِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3856,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:69","price":"他们必定会发现他们的祖先是迷误的，","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ أَلۡفَوۡاْ ءَابَآءَهُمۡ ضَآلِّينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3857,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:70","price":"他们却依着他们的踪迹而奔驰。","arabic":"فَهُمۡ عَلَىٰٓ ءَاثَٰرِهِمۡ يُهۡرَعُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3858,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:71","price":"在他们之前，大半的古人确已迷误了。","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ ضَلَّ قَبۡلَهُمۡ أَكۡثَرُ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3859,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:72","price":"我在他们之间，确已派遣过许多警告者。","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ أَرۡسَلۡنَا فِيهِم مُّنذِرِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3860,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:73","price":"你看！被警告者的结局是怎样的？","arabic":"فَٱنظُرۡ كَيۡفَ كَانَ عَٰقِبَةُ ٱلۡمُنذَرِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3861,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:74","price":"除非安拉的纯洁的仆人们。","arabic":"إِلَّا عِبَادَ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُخۡلَصِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3862,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:75","price":"努哈确已向我祈祷，我是最善于应答的！","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ نَادَىٰنَا نُوحٞ فَلَنِعۡمَ ٱلۡمُجِيبُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3863,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:76","price":"我拯救他和他的信徒们逃离大难。","arabic":"وَنَجَّيۡنَٰهُ وَأَهۡلَهُۥ مِنَ ٱلۡكَرۡبِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3864,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:77","price":"我只使他的子孙得以生存。","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا ذُرِّيَّتَهُۥ هُمُ ٱلۡبَاقِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3865,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:78","price":"我使他的令名，永存于后代。","arabic":"وَتَرَكۡنَا عَلَيۡهِ فِي ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3866,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:79","price":"在各民族中，都有人说：“祝努哈平安！”","arabic":"سَلَٰمٌ عَلَىٰ نُوحٖ فِي ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3867,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:80","price":"我必定要这样报酬行善者们。","arabic":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجۡزِي ٱلۡمُحۡسِنِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3868,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:81","price":"他确是我的信道的仆人。","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ مِنۡ عِبَادِنَا ٱلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3869,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:82","price":"然后，我使别的人淹死。","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَغۡرَقۡنَا ٱلۡأٓخَرِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3870,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:83","price":"他的宗派中，确有易卜拉欣。","arabic":"۞ وَإِنَّ مِن شِيعَتِهِۦ لَإِبۡرَٰهِيمَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3871,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:84","price":"当时，他带着健全的心灵，来见他的主。","arabic":"إِذۡ جَآءَ رَبَّهُۥ بِقَلۡبٖ سَلِيمٍ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3872,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:85","price":"当时，他对他的父亲和宗族说：“你们崇拜什么？","arabic":"إِذۡ قَالَ لِأَبِيهِ وَقَوۡمِهِۦ مَاذَا تَعۡبُدُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3873,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:86","price":"难道你们欲舍安拉而悖谬地崇拜许多神灵吗？","arabic":"أَئِفۡكًا ءَالِهَةٗ دُونَ ٱللَّهِ تُرِيدُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3874,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:87","price":"你们对众世界的主，究竟作什么猜测？”","arabic":"فَمَا ظَنُّكُم بِرَبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3875,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:88","price":"他看一看星宿，","arabic":"فَنَظَرَ نَظۡرَةٗ فِي ٱلنُّجُومِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3876,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:89","price":"然后说：“我势必要害病。”","arabic":"فَقَالَ إِنِّي سَقِيمٞ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3877,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:90","price":"他们就背离了他，","arabic":"فَتَوَلَّوۡاْ عَنۡهُ مُدۡبِرِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3878,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:91","price":"他就悄悄地走向他们的众神灵，他说：“你们怎么不吃东西呢？","arabic":"فَرَاغَ إِلَىٰٓ ءَالِهَتِهِمۡ فَقَالَ أَلَا تَأۡكُلُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3879,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:92","price":"你们怎么不说话呢？”","arabic":"مَا لَكُمۡ لَا تَنطِقُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3880,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:93","price":"他就悄悄地以右手打击他们。","arabic":"فَرَاغَ عَلَيۡهِمۡ ضَرۡبَۢا بِٱلۡيَمِينِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3881,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:94","price":"众人就急急忙忙地来看他，","arabic":"فَأَقۡبَلُوٓاْ إِلَيۡهِ يَزِفُّونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3882,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:95","price":"他说：“你们崇拜自己所雕刻的偶像吗？","arabic":"قَالَ أَتَعۡبُدُونَ مَا تَنۡحِتُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3883,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:96","price":"安拉创造你们，和你们的行为。”","arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ خَلَقَكُمۡ وَمَا تَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3884,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:97","price":"他们说：“你们应当为他而修一个火炉，然后将他投在烈火中。”","arabic":"قَالُواْ ٱبۡنُواْ لَهُۥ بُنۡيَٰنٗا فَأَلۡقُوهُ فِي ٱلۡجَحِيمِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3885,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:98","price":"他们欲谋害他，而我却使他们变成占下风的。","arabic":"فَأَرَادُواْ بِهِۦ كَيۡدٗا فَجَعَلۡنَٰهُمُ ٱلۡأَسۡفَلِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3886,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:99","price":"他说：“我果然要迁移到我的主所启示我的地方去，他将指导我。","arabic":"وَقَالَ إِنِّي ذَاهِبٌ إِلَىٰ رَبِّي سَيَهۡدِينِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3887,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:100","price":"我的主啊！求你赏赐我一个善良的儿子。”","arabic":"رَبِّ هَبۡ لِي مِنَ ٱلصَّٰلِحِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3888,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:101","price":"我就以一个宽厚的儿童向他报喜。","arabic":"فَبَشَّرۡنَٰهُ بِغُلَٰمٍ حَلِيمٖ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3889,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:102","price":"当他长到能帮着他操作的时候，他说：“我的小子啊！我确已梦见我宰你为牺牲。你考虑一下！你究竟有什么意见？”他说：“我的父亲啊！请你执行你所奉的命令吧！如果安拉意欲，你将发现我是坚忍的。”","arabic":"فَلَمَّا بَلَغَ مَعَهُ ٱلسَّعۡيَ قَالَ يَٰبُنَيَّ إِنِّيٓ أَرَىٰ فِي ٱلۡمَنَامِ أَنِّيٓ أَذۡبَحُكَ فَٱنظُرۡ مَاذَا تَرَىٰۚ قَالَ يَٰٓأَبَتِ ٱفۡعَلۡ مَا تُؤۡمَرُۖ سَتَجِدُنِيٓ إِن شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ مِنَ ٱلصَّٰبِرِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3890,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:103","price":"他俩既已顺服安拉，而他使他的儿子侧卧着。","arabic":"فَلَمَّآ أَسۡلَمَا وَتَلَّهُۥ لِلۡجَبِينِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3891,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:104","price":"我喊叫说：“易卜拉欣啊！","arabic":"وَنَٰدَيۡنَٰهُ أَن يَٰٓإِبۡرَٰهِيمُ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3892,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:105","price":"你确已证实那个梦了。”我必定要这样报酬行善的人们。","arabic":"قَدۡ صَدَّقۡتَ ٱلرُّءۡيَآۚ إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجۡزِي ٱلۡمُحۡسِنِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3893,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:106","price":"这确是明显的考验。","arabic":"إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَهُوَ ٱلۡبَلَٰٓؤُاْ ٱلۡمُبِينُ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3894,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:107","price":"我以一个伟大的牺牲赎了他。","arabic":"وَفَدَيۡنَٰهُ بِذِبۡحٍ عَظِيمٖ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3895,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:108","price":"我使他的令名，永存于后代。","arabic":"وَتَرَكۡنَا عَلَيۡهِ فِي ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3896,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:109","price":"“祝易卜拉欣平安！”","arabic":"سَلَٰمٌ عَلَىٰٓ إِبۡرَٰهِيمَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3897,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:110","price":"我这样报酬行善者。","arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ نَجۡزِي ٱلۡمُحۡسِنِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3898,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:111","price":"他确是我的信道的仆人，","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ مِنۡ عِبَادِنَا ٱلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3899,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:112","price":"我以将为先知和清廉者的易司哈格向他报喜。","arabic":"وَبَشَّرۡنَٰهُ بِإِسۡحَٰقَ نَبِيّٗا مِّنَ ٱلصَّٰلِحِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3900,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:113","price":"我降福于他和易司哈格。他俩的子孙中，将有行善者和公然自暴自弃者。","arabic":"وَبَٰرَكۡنَا عَلَيۡهِ وَعَلَىٰٓ إِسۡحَٰقَۚ وَمِن ذُرِّيَّتِهِمَا مُحۡسِنٞ وَظَالِمٞ لِّنَفۡسِهِۦ مُبِينٞ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3901,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:114","price":"我确已施恩于穆萨和哈伦。","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ مَنَنَّا عَلَىٰ مُوسَىٰ وَهَٰرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3902,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:115","price":"我曾使他俩及其宗族，得免于大难。","arabic":"وَنَجَّيۡنَٰهُمَا وَقَوۡمَهُمَا مِنَ ٱلۡكَرۡبِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3903,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:116","price":"我曾援助他们，所以他们是胜利者。","arabic":"وَنَصَرۡنَٰهُمۡ فَكَانُواْ هُمُ ٱلۡغَٰلِبِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3904,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:117","price":"我授予他俩详明的经典，","arabic":"وَءَاتَيۡنَٰهُمَا ٱلۡكِتَٰبَ ٱلۡمُسۡتَبِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3905,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:118","price":"我指引他俩正直的道路，","arabic":"وَهَدَيۡنَٰهُمَا ٱلصِّرَٰطَ ٱلۡمُسۡتَقِيمَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3906,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:119","price":"我使他俩的令名，永存于后代。","arabic":"وَتَرَكۡنَا عَلَيۡهِمَا فِي ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3907,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:120","price":"“祝穆萨和哈伦平安！”","arabic":"سَلَٰمٌ عَلَىٰ مُوسَىٰ وَهَٰرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3908,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:121","price":"我必定要这样报酬行善者。","arabic":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجۡزِي ٱلۡمُحۡسِنِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3909,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:122","price":"他俩确是我的信道的仆人。","arabic":"إِنَّهُمَا مِنۡ عِبَادِنَا ٱلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3910,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:123","price":"易勒雅斯确是使者。","arabic":"وَإِنَّ إِلۡيَاسَ لَمِنَ ٱلۡمُرۡسَلِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3911,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:124","price":"当时，他对他的宗族说：“难道你们不敬畏安拉吗？","arabic":"إِذۡ قَالَ لِقَوۡمِهِۦٓ أَلَا تَتَّقُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3912,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:125","price":"难道你们祈祷白耳利，而舍最优越的创造者——","arabic":"أَتَدۡعُونَ بَعۡلٗا وَتَذَرُونَ أَحۡسَنَ ٱلۡخَٰلِقِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3913,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:126","price":"安拉，你们的主，你们祖先的主吗？”","arabic":"ٱللَّهَ رَبَّكُمۡ وَرَبَّ ءَابَآئِكُمُ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3914,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:127","price":"他们否认他，所以他们必定要被拘禁。","arabic":"فَكَذَّبُوهُ فَإِنَّهُمۡ لَمُحۡضَرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3915,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:128","price":"惟安拉的纯洁的众仆则不然。","arabic":"إِلَّا عِبَادَ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُخۡلَصِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3916,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:129","price":"我使他的令名，永存后代。","arabic":"وَتَرَكۡنَا عَلَيۡهِ فِي ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3917,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:130","price":"“祝易勒雅斯平安！”","arabic":"سَلَٰمٌ عَلَىٰٓ إِلۡ يَاسِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3918,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:131","price":"我必定要这样报酬行善者。","arabic":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجۡزِي ٱلۡمُحۡسِنِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3919,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:132","price":"他确是我的信道的仆人。","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ مِنۡ عِبَادِنَا ٱلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3920,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:133","price":"鲁特确是使者。","arabic":"وَإِنَّ لُوطٗا لَّمِنَ ٱلۡمُرۡسَلِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3921,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:134","price":"当时，我拯救了他，和他的全体信徒；","arabic":"إِذۡ نَجَّيۡنَٰهُ وَأَهۡلَهُۥٓ أَجۡمَعِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3922,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:135","price":"惟有一个老妇人和其余的人，没有获得拯救。","arabic":"إِلَّا عَجُوزٗا فِي ٱلۡغَٰبِرِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3923,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:136","price":"然后，我毁灭了别的许多人。","arabic":"ثُمَّ دَمَّرۡنَا ٱلۡأٓخَرِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3924,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:137","price":"你们的确朝夕经过他们的遗迹，","arabic":"وَإِنَّكُمۡ لَتَمُرُّونَ عَلَيۡهِم مُّصۡبِحِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3925,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:138","price":"难道你们不了解吗？","arabic":"وَبِٱلَّيۡلِۚ أَفَلَا تَعۡقِلُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3926,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:139","price":"优努司确是使者。","arabic":"وَإِنَّ يُونُسَ لَمِنَ ٱلۡمُرۡسَلِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3927,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:140","price":"当时，他逃到那只满载的船舶上。","arabic":"إِذۡ أَبَقَ إِلَى ٱلۡفُلۡكِ ٱلۡمَشۡحُونِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3928,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:141","price":"他就拈阄，他却是失败的，","arabic":"فَسَاهَمَ فَكَانَ مِنَ ٱلۡمُدۡحَضِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3929,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:142","price":"大鱼就吞了他，同时，他是应受谴责的。","arabic":"فَٱلۡتَقَمَهُ ٱلۡحُوتُ وَهُوَ مُلِيمٞ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3930,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:143","price":"假若他不是常赞颂安拉者，","arabic":"فَلَوۡلَآ أَنَّهُۥ كَانَ مِنَ ٱلۡمُسَبِّحِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3931,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:144","price":"他必葬身鱼腹，直到世人复活之日。","arabic":"لَلَبِثَ فِي بَطۡنِهِۦٓ إِلَىٰ يَوۡمِ يُبۡعَثُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3932,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:145","price":"然后，我将他抛在旱地上，当时他是有病的。","arabic":"۞ فَنَبَذۡنَٰهُ بِٱلۡعَرَآءِ وَهُوَ سَقِيمٞ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3933,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:146","price":"我使一棵瓠瓜，长起来遮着他。","arabic":"وَأَنۢبَتۡنَا عَلَيۡهِ شَجَرَةٗ مِّن يَقۡطِينٖ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3934,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:147","price":"我曾派遣他去教化十多万民众。","arabic":"وَأَرۡسَلۡنَٰهُ إِلَىٰ مِاْئَةِ أَلۡفٍ أَوۡ يَزِيدُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3935,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:148","price":"他们便归信他，我使他们享乐至一个定期。","arabic":"فَـَٔامَنُواْ فَمَتَّعۡنَٰهُمۡ إِلَىٰ حِينٖ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3936,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:149","price":"你问他们吧！你的主有许多女儿，他们却有多少儿子呢？","arabic":"فَٱسۡتَفۡتِهِمۡ أَلِرَبِّكَ ٱلۡبَنَاتُ وَلَهُمُ ٱلۡبَنُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3937,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:150","price":"还是我曾将众天使造成女性的，他们曾眼见我的创造呢？","arabic":"أَمۡ خَلَقۡنَا ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةَ إِنَٰثٗا وَهُمۡ شَٰهِدُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3938,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:151","price":"真的，他们因为自己的悖谬，必定要说：","arabic":"أَلَآ إِنَّهُم مِّنۡ إِفۡكِهِمۡ لَيَقُولُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3939,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:152","price":"“安拉已生育了。”他们确是说谎者。","arabic":"وَلَدَ ٱللَّهُ وَإِنَّهُمۡ لَكَٰذِبُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3940,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:153","price":"难道他不要儿子，却要女儿吗？","arabic":"أَصۡطَفَى ٱلۡبَنَاتِ عَلَى ٱلۡبَنِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3941,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:154","price":"你们有什么理由？你们怎么这样判断呢？","arabic":"مَا لَكُمۡ كَيۡفَ تَحۡكُمُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3942,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:155","price":"你们还不觉悟吗？","arabic":"أَفَلَا تَذَكَّرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3943,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:156","price":"难道你们有一个明证吗？","arabic":"أَمۡ لَكُمۡ سُلۡطَٰنٞ مُّبِينٞ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3944,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:157","price":"拿出你们的经典来吧，倘若你们是诚实的人！","arabic":"فَأۡتُواْ بِكِتَٰبِكُمۡ إِن كُنتُمۡ صَٰدِقِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3945,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:158","price":"他们妄言他与精灵之间，有姻亲关系。精灵确已知道他们将被拘禁","arabic":"وَجَعَلُواْ بَيۡنَهُۥ وَبَيۡنَ ٱلۡجِنَّةِ نَسَبٗاۚ وَلَقَدۡ عَلِمَتِ ٱلۡجِنَّةُ إِنَّهُمۡ لَمُحۡضَرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3946,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:159","price":"——超绝哉安拉！他是超乎他们的叙述的","arabic":"سُبۡحَٰنَ ٱللَّهِ عَمَّا يَصِفُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3947,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:160","price":"惟安拉的虔诚的众仆，","arabic":"إِلَّا عِبَادَ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُخۡلَصِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3948,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:161","price":"你们和你们所崇拜的，","arabic":"فَإِنَّكُمۡ وَمَا تَعۡبُدُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3949,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:162","price":"绝不能把任何人引诱去崇拜他们，","arabic":"مَآ أَنتُمۡ عَلَيۡهِ بِفَٰتِنِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3950,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:163","price":"除非是将入火狱的人。","arabic":"إِلَّا مَنۡ هُوَ صَالِ ٱلۡجَحِيمِ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3951,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:164","price":"（众天使说）：“我们人人都有一个指定的地位，","arabic":"وَمَا مِنَّآ إِلَّا لَهُۥ مَقَامٞ مَّعۡلُومٞ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3952,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:165","price":"我们必定是排班的，","arabic":"وَإِنَّا لَنَحۡنُ ٱلصَّآفُّونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3953,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:166","price":"我们必定是赞颂安拉的。”","arabic":"وَإِنَّا لَنَحۡنُ ٱلۡمُسَبِّحُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3954,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:167","price":"他们的确常说：","arabic":"وَإِن كَانُواْ لَيَقُولُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3955,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:168","price":"“假若我们有古人所遗留的教诲，","arabic":"لَوۡ أَنَّ عِندَنَا ذِكۡرٗا مِّنَ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3956,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:169","price":"那么，我们必是安拉的纯洁的仆人。”","arabic":"لَكُنَّا عِبَادَ ٱللَّهِ ٱلۡمُخۡلَصِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3957,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:170","price":"他们却不信安拉，他们不久就知道了。","arabic":"فَكَفَرُواْ بِهِۦۖ فَسَوۡفَ يَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3958,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:171","price":"我对我所派遣的仆人们已约言在先了，","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ سَبَقَتۡ كَلِمَتُنَا لِعِبَادِنَا ٱلۡمُرۡسَلِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3959,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:172","price":"他们必定是被援助的，","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ لَهُمُ ٱلۡمَنصُورُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3960,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:173","price":"我的军队，必定是胜利的。","arabic":"وَإِنَّ جُندَنَا لَهُمُ ٱلۡغَٰلِبُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3961,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:174","price":"你暂时退避他们吧！","arabic":"فَتَوَلَّ عَنۡهُمۡ حَتَّىٰ حِينٖ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3962,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:175","price":"你看着吧！他们不久就看见了。","arabic":"وَأَبۡصِرۡهُمۡ فَسَوۡفَ يُبۡصِرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3963,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:176","price":"难道他们要求我的刑罚早日实现吗？","arabic":"أَفَبِعَذَابِنَا يَسۡتَعۡجِلُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3964,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:177","price":"我的刑罚一旦降于他们的庭院的时候，被警告者的早晨，真恶劣呀！","arabic":"فَإِذَا نَزَلَ بِسَاحَتِهِمۡ فَسَآءَ صَبَاحُ ٱلۡمُنذَرِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3965,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:178","price":"你暂时退避他们吧！","arabic":"وَتَوَلَّ عَنۡهُمۡ حَتَّىٰ حِينٖ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3966,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:179","price":"你看着吧！他们不久就看见了。","arabic":"وَأَبۡصِرۡ فَسَوۡفَ يُبۡصِرُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3967,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:180","price":"超绝哉你的主——尊荣的主宰！他是超乎他们的叙述的。","arabic":"سُبۡحَٰنَ رَبِّكَ رَبِّ ٱلۡعِزَّةِ عَمَّا يَصِفُونَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3968,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:181","price":"祝众使者平安！","arabic":"وَسَلَٰمٌ عَلَى ٱلۡمُرۡسَلِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3969,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"},{"name":"37:182","price":"一切赞颂，全归安拉——养育众世界的主！","arabic":"وَٱلۡحَمۡدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat"],"ayahNumber":3970,"juzNumber":23,"footnotes":"","lang":"zh"}],"chapter":["37 (As-Saffat)","As-Saffat","Surah As-Saffat","Chapter As-Saffat","Saffat","Surah Saffat","Chapter Saffat","As Saffat","Surah As Saffat","Chapter As Saffat","Surah 37","Chapter 37","Those Who Set The Ranks","الصَّافَات"]}